      "Anyone initializes epoch 1 (manually or via the first epoch-1 deposit/withdraw), so `poolSize[token][1]` is copied from the forged zero snapshot.",
      "An epoch-0 staker withdraws in epoch 1 and hits `poolSize[token][1].size.sub(amount)`, which can revert because the pool snapshot was zeroed."
